in the middle of the night

00:11:24,950 --> 00:11:27,053
to go on
a midnight doughnut run

00:11:27,186 --> 00:11:30,122
instead of terrorizing them
the way I used to.

00:11:30,256 --> 00:11:33,025
So that's what I thought
tonight's topic would be.

00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:37,263
How do we look for happiness
and get out of our own way...

00:11:37,396 --> 00:11:40,499
now that we don't drink anymore?

00:11:40,633 --> 00:11:42,301
