00:11:42,435 --> 00:11:44,370
[GROUP APPLAUDS]

00:11:45,638 --> 00:11:47,373
Would anybody like to start?

00:11:50,509 --> 00:11:51,644
Okay.

00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:56,215
Hi, my name is Lexie,
and I'm an alcoholic.

00:11:56,348 --> 00:11:58,184
GROUP:
Hi, Lexie.

00:11:58,317 --> 00:12:01,287
